<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟku yāṇṭu 4<g type="dash"/>Āvatu keraḷān=ta kavaḷanāṭṭu <unclear>Uṟaiyūrkkūṟ</unclear>ṟattu tiruvaṭakuṭi <hi rend="grantha">ma</hi>
