<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉukku vaitta kalam 1 Ikkala(m) <unclear>m</unclear>oṉṟukkum Ivvūr maṇaṟkāṭup puṉce <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
